{"tid":1537714,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[突發][接力]富士山山頂再度出現革命旗幟","createTime":"2019-09-04T04:25:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-15T03:02:09.000Z","uid":129571,"like":66,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"ee8bf44812f0c289bdd00556c1acb9c01518ad8b","tid":1537714,"uid":129571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T04:25:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/q9BWvrU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fq9BWvrU.jpg&h=172b03ca&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xpdNB61.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxpdNB61.jpg&h=17153d97&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n相信呢兩日大家都睇到唔少巴絲手足們上富士山插旗 有幾位仲早過我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過正所謂兄弟爬山 各自努力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 日日都要有革命旗係山頂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n上到富士山當然要用埋日文做文宣 同日本人宣傳下<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同場加映強國玻璃心三毛係神社寫ge繪馬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35433bb8546b92ea3d57c562af2b6036e077ccaf","tid":1537714,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T04:25:43.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n烏克蘭, 法國等其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮, 唔割但要小心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外可參考唔揸春袋揸輸精管方法: <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n [行動p